text.tspan: Nitrous oxide emissions by sector (Gg CO₂e), World
Breakdown of total global nitrous oxide (N₂O) emissions by sector, measured in gigagrams of carbon-dioxide
equivalents (CO₂e). Carbon dioxide equivalents measures the total greenhouse gas potential of the full combination
of gases, weighted by their relative warming impacts.
Source: UN Food and Agricultural Organization (FAO)
